### 购物车库存校验和锁定接口测试

@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{loginData.token}}

### 1. 批量校验库存接口测试
# @name checkStock
POST {{host}}/api/cart/check-stock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

[
  {
    "productId": 1,
    "quantity": 1
  },
  {
    "productId": 2,
    "quantity": 2
  }
]

### 2. 批量锁定库存接口测试
# @name lockStock
POST {{host}}/api/cart/lock-stock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

[
  {
    "productId": 1,
    "quantity": 1
  },
  {
    "productId": 2,
    "quantity": 2
  }
]

### 3. 获取购物车列表（验证库存锁定后的数据）
GET {{host}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
